            <bug_when>2010-01-18 12:41:41 +0000</bug_when>
            <thetext>The build script attempts to get the revision number and insert it into a properties file to make it possible to trace which revision of the source tree binaries were built from. See the target -hg-get-changeset in build.xml. However, this target gets the revision number for tip, not for the current revision of the working copy.

We should use &quot;hg identify --id&quot; instead of &quot;hg log -r tip&quot; to get the correct revision number.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
